title: Dungen - Tio Bitar [2007]
description:
Dungen Tio bitar - 2007

2007 album from the critically-adored Swedish outfit, led by the musical madness of Gustav Ejstes, who combine gorgeous melodies with their own modern slant on Psychedelia. Dungen's music is sweet and somber one moment, electrifying and elegant the next, but is never less than fascinating. 10 tracks including 'Gor Det Nu' and 'Mon Amour'. Subliminal Sounds. --This text refers to an out of print or unavailable edition of this title.
